data.description: Downtown Greer, less then 2 miles from GSP, 2.5 miles from BMW, and close to I85 and Greer Hospital. This Modern style home has been fully updated. From new lighting, can lights and bathroom updates.  It has 3 bedrooms and 2 full baths. It has plenty of space. It has a Beautiful exterior back deck and a beautiful paver patio with plenty of sitting space to make special family memories and gatherings. The home has beautiful laminate floors through out the open areas and master bedroom. This home has an amazing living room area with a black vaulted ceiling that makes the space stand out. So many special custom touches makes this home so special and beautiful. This home is perfect for your family. Come on out and enjoy taking a look at this property.
